Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:44.40,EDEN,,0,0,0,,♪ Gotta get back ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.32,EDEN,,0,0,0,,♪ Back to the past ♪
